Cryptocurrency pump represent a situation where group of persons plans to make a profit by pumping an asset into the market. The term “pumping” is used to indicate the purchasing of large quantities of coins to push the demand and price of respective coin UP.

There are a lot of big exchanges like Binance, KuCoin, FTX, Kraken e t c. We work on PancakeSwap (LINK ON COINMARKETCAP).
